imdb.plot outline: Like many women over 50, CHARLENE GRAY is starting to feel invisible. And strange things are happening around her, all leading to the reappearance of RANDY BUSH, Charlene's former neighbor and one time reigning Adult Film Superstar. Randy, larger than life, just happens to be dead, and is meeting all kinds of interesting folks in the great beyond, with helpful ideas to bring Charlene's mojo back.
